@@TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper
Summary
  Basic character mapping class.
Description
  TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper is the basic character mapping class. For each digit class a
  character mapper class is created which will contain the default mapping (note: sometimes digit
  classes may share the same mapper, for example when two digit classes have other style segments but
  segment layout remains the same).

  The class provides in methods to map a text to it's segment representation, stream mappings in or
  out and changing mappings.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.Clear
Summary
  Clears the mappings table.
Description
  Clear empties the character mapping table. After a call to clear, no character will map to any
  segment (i.e. all characters map effectively to a space).
See Also
  TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.LoadFromStream, TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.SaveToStream

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.CurDigit
Summary
  Current digit for which we are mapping.
Description
