----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.LoadFromFile
Summary
  Loads a character mapping from a file.
Description
  LoadFromFile will read a character mapping from the specified file and applies that to the mapping
  table.

  LoadFromFile internally creates a TFileStream and calls LoadFromStream on that stream.
Parameters
  FileName - File name of the mapping to load.
See Also
  TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.LoadFromStream, TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.SaveToFile

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.LoadFromStream
Summary
  Reads a character mapping from a stream.
Description
  LoadFromStream will read a character mapping from the specified stream and applies it to the
  mapping table.

  If the current position of the stream does not refer to a valid mapping for this mapper class, an
  exception is raised (the stream position will not have changed nor will the mapping table be
  changed).

  Before reading of the actual mapping, the table is first cleared with a call to Clear. Next the
  data from the stream is read for each mapped character and applies to the mapping table.
Parameters
  Stream - Stream from which to read the mapping table. Reading starts at the current position of
        the stream. If the stream points to an invalid mapping, the position will not have
            changed. After reading the stream's position is updated to point to the first byte
            following the mapping.
See Also
  TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.LoadFromFile, TJvBaseSegmentedLEDCharacterMapper.SaveToStream

